text: Trevor Schwab of Avon and his hunting crew donated three deer hides to our Hides for Habitat program this weekend! It might not seem like a big deal, but IT IS! The money raised from collecting deer hides goes right back into creating better habitat for deer and other wildlife! #recycling #recycledmaterials #deerhunting
I love seeing those hides boxes! Came across these ones in Big Lake, Motley and Hackensack Longville and Pine River. Proud to be an MDHA member!!!

text: I'm a sustaining member and you can become one, too for as little as $5!!!

We're still looking for volunteers to help set up from 11-4! Message me if you're interested in helping, even if it's for an hour of two! :-)

BANQUET / HABITAT BUCKS ALERT!! Only two days to register & purchase your Habitat Bucks for a discounted rate. If purchased by August 7th $140 Habitat Bucks for $100, if purchased at the Banquet $120 Habitat Bucks for $100 or $60 Habitat Bucks for $50. Feel free to email Terry at terrylydell@qualityci.us with any questions.
